{"name":"Ring of Control Humans","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<ul>\n<li><strong>Usage:</strong> A charm may be placed upon a human within 60′. One target may be charmed per round.</li>\n<li><strong>Resisting:</strong> The subject may <strong>save versus spells (with a &ndash;2 penalty)</strong> to resist.</li>\n<li><strong>Maximum subjects:</strong> Up to 6 Hit Dice of humans may be charmed in this way. Normal humans count as &frac12; HD.</li>\n<li><strong>Charmed individuals:</strong> Regard the character as a trusted friend, and will come to their defence. They will obey the character&rsquo;s commands, as long as these are not obviously harmful and do not contradict the subject&rsquo;s alignment.</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> The charm lasts until dispelled, until the ring is removed, or until the wearer cancels it.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"0zEk8suZA1vpNX4o"}
{"name":"Ring of Wishes, 1-3","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Grants the wearer&rsquo;s wishes (see <a title=\"Magic Items (General)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Magic_Items_(General)#Wishes\">Wishes</a>).</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Charges:</strong> The number of wishes granted is noted in the <em><strong>Rings</strong></em> table. Once all wishes have been used, the ring&rsquo;s magic is spent.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"4ecMheeXBIYVEDen"}
{"name":"Ring of Fire Resistance","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Grants the wearer protection against fire.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Normal fire:</strong> Unharmed by non-magical fire.</li>\n<li><strong>Save bonus:</strong> Gain a +2 bonus to all saving throws versus fire-based magical or breath attacks.</li>\n<li><strong>Fire-based damage:</strong> Is reduced by 1 point per damage die rolled. (Each die inflicts a minimum of 1 hit point damage.)</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"6qtJmnYPHAtApdwX"}
{"name":"Ring of Spell Storing","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Stores a number of magical spells that the wearer can release on command.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Capacity:</strong> The ring contains 1d6 spells. (The spells can be triggered and recharged, but cannot be changed.)</li>\n<li><strong>Type of magic:</strong> There is a 20% chance of divine spells, otherwise they are arcane spells.</li>\n<li><strong>Knowledge:</strong> The wearer of the ring knows which spells it contains.</li>\n<li><strong>Triggering:</strong> The wearer of the ring can trigger the spells at will (up to one spell per round).</li>\n<li><strong>Caster level:</strong> For spells whose effects vary by the level of the caster, the wearer of the ring is treated as a caster of the lowest level required to cast the spell.</li>\n<li><strong>Recharging:</strong> Once a spell is triggered, it may not be reused until it is recharged&mdash;the expired spell must be cast directly onto the ring.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"8YT5ke71BugKXybH"}
{"name":"Ring of Wishes, 2-4","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Grants the wearer&rsquo;s wishes (see <a title=\"Magic Items (General)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Magic_Items_(General)#Wishes\">Wishes</a>).</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Charges:</strong> The number of wishes granted is noted in the <em><strong>Rings</strong></em> table. Once all wishes have been used, the ring&rsquo;s magic is spent.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"APH03JyNplFnl7Kl"}
{"name":"Ring of Protection +1 (5’ rad)","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Grants a measure of protection from harm:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Armour Class:</strong> A +1 AC bonus.</li>\n<li><strong>Saving throws:</strong> A +1 bonus to all saves.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span id=\"Ring_of_Protection,_5′_Radius\"></span><strong><span id=\"Ring_of_Protection.2C_5.E2.80.99_Radius\" class=\"mw-headline\">Ring of Protection, 5′ Radius:</span></strong></p>\n<p>Allies within 5′ of the wearer also benefit from the ring&rsquo;s protective power. For example, two characters fighting beside the wearer of the ring would gain the protective benefit.&nbsp;</p>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"AT2InXj8kbgk8eBS"}
{"name":"Ring of Telekinesis","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Grants the power to move objects or creatures within 120′ by concentrating.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Weight:</strong> Up to 2,000 coins of weight may be targeted.</li>\n<li><strong>Movement:</strong> The target may be moved up to 20′ per round, in whatever direction the wearer of the ring wishes (including vertically).</li>\n<li><strong>Resisting:</strong> A targeted creature may <strong>save versus spells</strong> to resist.</li>\n<li><strong>Concentration:</strong> If concentration is broken, the target falls.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"BnlEjv75pOXOTOO1"}
{"name":"Ring of Regeneration","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>The wearer heals at an accelerated rate.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Rate:</strong> The wearer regains 1 hit point per round.</li>\n<li><strong>Severed limbs:</strong> Will also regrow. The rate depends on the size of the limb (e.g. a finger may regrow in one day, while a whole limb may take a week).</li>\n<li><strong>Fire or acid damage:</strong> Cannot be regenerated.</li>\n<li><strong>Death:</strong> The ring does not function if the wearer is reduced to 0 or less hit points.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"CAgRK8H2AuqYtbqa"}
{"name":"Ring of Djinni Summoning","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>This ring grants the power to summon a <a title=\"Djinni (Lesser)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Djinni_(Lesser)\">djinni</a>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Duration of service:</strong> The djinni will serve the character who summoned it for up to 24 hours.</li>\n<li><strong>Commands:</strong> The djinni only obeys the one who summoned it&mdash;another character who takes the ring has no power over the djinni.</li>\n<li><strong>Usage frequency:</strong> The ring may be used up to once per day.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"DAxrArXRYu3Fr1Cc"}
{"name":"Ring of X-Ray Vision","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Grants the power to see through solid objects.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Through dense materials:</strong> Sight up to 60′ through less dense materials (cloth, water, wood) is possible.</li>\n<li><strong>Through stone:</strong> Sight up to 30′ through stone is possible.</li>\n<li><strong>Obstructions:</strong> Sight through gold or lead is blocked.</li>\n<li><strong>Searching:</strong> When used for the purpose of searching (see <a title=\"Dungeon Adventuring\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Dungeon_Adventuring\">Dungeon Adventuring</a>), the wearer is guaranteed to notice secret doors or traps in the 10′ square area being examined.</li>\n<li><strong>Concentration:</strong> Using the ring requires concentration (the wearer cannot move).</li>\n<li><strong>Usage frequency:</strong> May be used at most once per turn.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"FS91azz501JKG954"}
{"name":"Ring of Water Walking","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Grants the power to walk on the surface of water, without sinking.&nbsp;</p>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"R1imPJHFtKxKPWrs"}
{"name":"Ring of Control Animals","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Grants the power to control the actions of animals.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Affects:</strong> 1d6 normal animals or 1 giant animal (not magical or intelligent animals).</li>\n<li><strong>Resisting:</strong> No saving throw is allowed.</li>\n<li><strong>Visual range:</strong> The character can only control animals that they can see.</li>\n<li><strong>Concentration:</strong> Control is broken if the user of the ring moves or attacks.</li>\n<li><strong>When concentration ends:</strong> The referee should make a reaction roll with a &ndash;1 penalty (see <a title=\"Encounters\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Encounters\">Encounters</a>) to determine the animals&rsquo; behaviour.</li>\n<li><strong>Usage frequency:</strong> May be used up to once per turn.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"TgXxKM0M32Lq7I1p"}
{"name":"Ring of Delusion","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>The wearer believes is under the effects of another type of magic ring.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Type:</strong> The other type of ring should be determined by the referee (e.g. a ring of protection or a ring of spell turning).</li>\n<li><strong>Describing:</strong> The referee should try to trick the player into believing that the character is under the effects of the other ring, only revealing the truth at some vital juncture.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"UAwvlJpNeP29Tu2W"}
{"name":"Ring of Control Plants","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Grants the power to control plants.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Affects:</strong> All plants (including plant monsters) in a 10′ square area.</li>\n<li><strong>Range:</strong> The area may be up to 60′ distant.</li>\n<li><strong>Commands:</strong> Affected plants may be commanded to move around as the character wishes.</li>\n<li><strong>Concentration:</strong> The effect lasts as long as the wearer of the ring concentrates.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"W749CtXUDAkgeTDQ"}
{"name":"Ring of Spell Turning","permission":{"default":0,"A408mJC8WC2SaXfR":3},"type":"item","data":{"description":"<p>Spells cast on the wearer of this ring are reflected back onto the caster.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Charges:</strong> After 2d6 spells are reflected, the ring loses its power.</li>\n</ul>","quantity":{"value":1,"max":0},"treasure":false,"cost":0,"weight":0},"flags":{},"img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-band-engraved-scrolls-gold.webp","effects":[],"_id":"g4sCdokvNh5imrju"}
